{"name": "md-caba", "metadata": {"name": "md-caba", "version": "0.1.2", "classifiers": ["License :: OSI Approved :: MIT License", "Operating System :: OS Independent", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3"], "home_page": "https://github.com/CaBa52052/md_caba", "license": null, "documentation_url": null, "dependencies": ["markdown"], "summary": "\u4e00\u4e2a\u7b80\u5355\u7684Markdown\u6587\u4ef6\u8bfb\u53d6\u548c\u89e3\u6790\u5de5\u5177", "upload_time": 1733939761}, "documentation": ["# MD CaBa\r\n\r\n\u4e00\u4e2a\u7b80\u5355\u7684Markdown\u6587\u4ef6\u8bfb\u53d6\u548c\u89e3\u6790\u5de5\u5177\u3002\r\n\r\n## \u5b89\u88c5\r\n\r\n```bash\r\npip install md_caba\r\n```\r\n\r\n## \u4f7f\u7528\u65b9\u6cd5\r\n\r\n```python\r\nfrom md_caba import MDReader\r\n\r\n# \u521b\u5efaMDReader\u5b9e\u4f8b\r\nreader = MDReader('path/to/your/file.md')\r\n\r\n# \u83b7\u53d6\u6240\u6709\u4ee3\u7801\u5757\r\ncode_blocks = reader.get_code_blocks()\r\n\r\n# \u83b7\u53d6\u7279\u5b9a\u8bed\u8a00\u7684\u4ee3\u7801\u5757\r\npython_blocks = reader.get_code_blocks('python')\r\n\r\n# \u6253\u5370\u6240\u6709\u5185\u5bb9\r\nreader.print_content()\r\n\r\n# \u8f6c\u6362\u4e3aJSON\r\njson_content = reader.to_json()\r\n``` \r\n"], "modules": [{"name": "md_caba", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [{"name": "md_caba.__version__", "type": null, "documentation": []}], "classes": [], "exports": [{"name": "md_caba.MDReader", "xref": {"fqname": "md_caba.core.MDReader", "project": null}}]}, {"name": "md_caba.core", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [{"name": "md_caba.core.MDReader", "bases": [], "methods": [{"name": "md_caba.core.MDReader.__init__", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "md_caba.core.MDReader._extract_code_blocks", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": ["\u63d0\u53d6\u6240\u